in a haystack: a tiny dome in
pre-war satellite

34:49.454 --> 34:51.356 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
images of Aleppo.

34:51.456 --> 34:56.962 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
