go through regular resiliency
training.

35:52.784 --> 35:57.355 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SAM DUBBERLEY: Just watching a
video without
sound is actually less
distressing than watching

35:57.455 --> 35:58.923 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
