real business.

50:04.068 --> 50:05.603 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes.

50:05.703 --> 50:10.107 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TOMMY HILFIGER: And I wanted to
distinguish
my look from everyone else's.

50:10.207 --> 50:14.678 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
