preppy clothes
I had worn as a very young boy.

50:22.686 --> 50:24.555 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I thought they were very
boring and very
tired.

50:24.655 --> 50:27.291 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
