50:31.896 --> 50:33.931 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I didn't like the feel of the
fabric.

50:34.031 --> 50:38.335 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I didn't like that it was too
mediocre, so
to speak.

50:38.435 --> 50:44.475 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, I thought, I'm going to make
everything,
like, relaxed, colorful,
detailed.

50:44.575 --> 50:47.111 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But I wanted to build it for a
broad audience.

50:47.211 --> 50:51.715 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
